snippet.title: Mermaid Secrets12 - Heartbreak Love Story by JoyPlus Tech ( Premiere  Version)
snippet.description:
Mermaid Secrets12 - Heartbreak Love Story by JoyPlus Tech

iOS link: 
https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/mermaid-secrets12-heartbreak/id1367771120?mt=8

Google Link: 
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=net.joyplustech.android_mermaid12


High school boy Eric asked Mermaid Mia go out for picnic! Now get a makeover before your date. Oh, no.The mean girl Kim is following you. Be careful! God knows what will she do?
Watch out! Mia was pushed into the water again. OMG! She was caught by the net.Please save mermaid right now. WHAT? Kim wants to post mermaid princess Mia’s video. Stop it right now! It's time for mermaid princess Mia to fight this arrogant girl. 

Features:
1. Kim collected the mermaid’s fish scale and wanted to find the answer in the library.
2. OMG! There is a book which revealed the secrets for a mermaid princess.
3. Kim plans to find a chance to push mermaid Mia into the water again, then mermaid’s secrets will be exposed.
4. Yay – Your Crush Eric asked you out for picnic! Get a makeover before your date. 
5. How sweet – he got you a special gift. It was made by himself. 
6. Get ready to fall in love with the cutest boy in school!
7. Time for the best date EVER! You may even get your first kiss…
8. The mean girl in high school is following you. Be careful! God knows what will she do? 
9. Watch out! Mia was pushed into the water again. OMG! She was caught by a net in the lake. Please save mermaid right now.
10.WHAT? The mean girl Kim wants to post mermaid princess Mia’s video Stop it right now. It's time for you to fight this arrogant girl. 
11. Can you delete the video? No. Come to my house and I will do what you request. 
12. Romantic lights, beautiful music even candles! What are Eric and Kim talking about? They seem have a good time. Will Eric left me? 

The best Mysterious and Romantic mermaid love storyever! Download Free Now!
